commit.message: switch to no-arg super() calls

Drop Python 2 support

Polyfield depends on Marshmallow 3 which requires at least Python 3.5.

Bachmann1234/marshmallow-polyfield#35
Twine's check function did not check this field so it exploded when I tried to upload
The license field should just be a single line describing the license
Fix warning about keywords
Increment version
Add kwargs args to decorated post_load methods to be consistent with updated marshmallow api

Add `kwargs` to `_[de]serialize(...)

This seems to be a recent change in marshmallow but is shown in the docs
at
https://marshmallow.readthedocs.io/en/3.0/custom_fields.html#creating-a-field-class
Based on a trick nicoddemus showed me over on diff-cover I think this will only try and publish once rather than a race to see who publishes first :-P
